    {
        "content": "<p>madsmtm created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13137#discussion_r3106803402\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Another design for this could be to take:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">segment</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">String</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"n\">section</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">String</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"n\">macho_section_type</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">String</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"n\">macho_section_attributes</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Vec</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nb\">String</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>And then have the \"pure_instructions\" -&gt; S_ATTR_PURE_INSTRUCTIONS mapping in <code>cranelift-object</code>? What would you prefer?</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 586360349,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1776601006
    },
