    {
        "content": "<p>bjorn3 created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13137#discussion_r3113321558\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Actually shouldn't this be <code>|=</code>? As is this would overwrite the default flags even when no flags are passed.</p>\n</blockquote>",
