    },
    {
        "content": "<p>bjorn3 created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13137#discussion_r3113401354\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Would skipping the flag set if macho_flags is 0 makes sense?</p>\n</blockquote>",
