    {
        "content": "<p>madsmtm submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13137#pullrequestreview-4143152775\">PR review</a>.</p>",
        "id": 588473261,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1776716073
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>madsmtm created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13137#discussion_r3113402081\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Maybe we could do:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">section_type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">macho_flags</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">SECTION_TYPE</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">section_attributes</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">macho_flags</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">SECTION_ATTRIBUTES</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">current_attributes</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">flags</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">SECTION_ATTRIBUTES</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">flags</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">section_type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">current_attributes</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">section_attributes</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>But I feared that might be confusing too, if I request only <code>no_dead_strip</code>, it might be weird if I got other attributes too.</p>\n<p>Though we should probably have an assert that <code>*flags</code> is <code>0</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 588473263,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1776716074
